            <abstract>
                <p>This astrological text contains descriptions of the twelve zodiac signs, including their positions in the sky and their astrological characteristics. Each description of a zodiac sign concludes with a separate section on women.
                    The text demonstrates a fairly stable structure, but there is relatively high variability in wording across different manuscripts.</p>
